          <h3 class="hd3 text-center">Community</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">Join a diverse community of users who share ideas, provide feedback, and collaborate.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-8">
    <div class="p-6">
      <h2 class="hd2">Our Technology</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        We're proud to build on cutting-edge technologies that provide a robust, secure, and delightful user experience:
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Rails 8</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">The latest version of Ruby on Rails powers our backend, providing a solid foundation for rapid development and reliable performance.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Tailwind CSS</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Our user interface is built with Tailwind CSS, enabling a responsive, accessible, and visually consistent design system.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Hotwire</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We use Hotwire to create fast, dynamic interfaces without the complexity of a full JavaScript framework.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">PostgreSQL</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Our data is stored in PostgreSQL, a powerful, open-source database known for its reliability and advanced features.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
